Class Runner

java.lang.Object
ie.atu.sw.Runner
public class Runner extends Object
Since:
21 This java application uses console-based menu-driven UI to input the path to the lexicon(s) that user wish to use and the path to the Twitter / X users(s) to process, produce a sentiment score for each tweet or (in future development) by user choice an overall score of all the tweets.
